{"tid":814022,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"花1200萬向內地等推廣「深水埗自助遊」　旅發局林建岳：不影響當區物價","createTime":"2018-09-11T01:55:06.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-11T05:53:14.000Z","uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":55,"uniUserReply":35,"replies":[{"pid":"92e4528053466a0d7081afc5e0cc0e86e1634ae2","tid":814022,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-11T01:55:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/ssp_Y54WX_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2Fssp_Y54WX_1200x0.png&h=081dc159&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n旅發局圖片<br />\n<br />\n政府去年公布本港貧窮情況，深水埗是十八區貧窮率最高的地區，該區劏房情況亦受不少國際媒體關注。旅發局今日宣布投放逾1,200萬元，集中推廣深水埗，推出「香港 &middot; 大城小區 - 深水埗」項目，向包括內地等的旅客宣傳，並邀請深水埗多間「傳統及新型特色小店」參與。<br />\n<br />\n旅發局今日深水埗福華街舉行活動推廣舉行啟動儀式，主席林建岳指，是次推廣項目花費逾1200萬，比去年「舊城中環」項目要多，主因增加在內地地區宣傳。林又陷為，遊客在區內消費能有助各行各業，相信不會對當區物價、人流承載量帶來太大影響，「唔會影響到&hellip;&hellip;推高個expense」。<br />\n<br />\n出席活動的商務及經濟發展局局長邱騰華稱，相信活動能夠豐富訪港旅客的旅遊體驗。<br />\n<br />\n旅發局表示，將會推出介紹深水埗的廣告和微電影，以及與業界合作推出更多區內導賞團。旅發局亦推出印刷版及網上電子版的深水埗自助遊漫步指南，推介約65個特色地點。旅客可在掃瞄深水埗街道指示牌上的QR Code，便可瀏覽有關指南。旅發局會在深水埗港鐵站、區內燈柱、電箱及欄干添置「紅白藍帆布」圖案及鈕扣等裝飾，指有助突顯深水埗區內特色。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/society/%E8%8A%B11200%E8%90%AC%E5%90%91%E5%85%A7%E5%9C%B0%E7%AD%89%E6%8E%A8%E5%BB%A3-%E6%B7%B1%E6%B0%B4%E5%9F%97%E8%87%AA%E5%8A%A9%E9%81%8A-%E6%97%85%E7%99%BC%E5%B1%80%E6%9E%97%E5%BB%BA%E5%B2%B3-%E4%B8%8D%E5%BD%B1%E9%9F%BF%E7%95%B6%E5%8D%80%E7%89%A9%E5%83%B9/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fsociety%2F%25E8%258A%25B11200%25E8%2590%25AC%25E5%2590%2591%25E5%2585%25A7%25E5%259C%25B0%25E7%25AD%2589%25E6%258E%25A8%25E5%25BB%25A3-%25E6%25B7%25B1%25E6%25B0%25B4%25E5%259F%2597%25E8%2587%25AA%25E5%258A%25A9%25E9%2581%258A-%25E6%2597%2585%25E7%2599%25BC%25E5%25B1%2580%25E6%259E%2597%25E5%25BB%25BA%25E5%25B2%25B3-%25E4%25B8%258D%25E5%25BD%25B1%25E9%259F%25BF%25E7%2595%25B6%25E5%258D%2580%25E7%2589%25A9%25E5%2583%25B9%2F&d=FUuYnxO0i5%2Bxzp683N%2F9HozZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=8a0262eb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fsociety%2F%25E8%258A%25B11200%25E8%2590%25AC%25E5%2590%2591%25E5%2585%25A7%25E5%259C%25B0%25E7%25AD%2589%25E6%258E%25A8%25E5%25BB%25A3-%25E6%25B7%25B1%25E6%25B0%25B4%25E5%259F%2597%25E8%2587%25AA%25E5%258A%25A9%25E9%2581%258A-%25E6%2597%2585%25E7%2599%25BC%25E5%25B1%2580%25E6%259E%2597%25E5%25BB%25BA%25E5%25B2%25B3-%25E4%25B8%258D%25E5%25BD%25B1%25E9%259F%25BF%25E7%2595%25B6%25E5%258D%2580%25E7%2589%25A9%25E5%2583%25B9%2F&h=26348c06\" target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/society/%E8%8A%B11200%E8%90%AC%E5%90%91%E5%85%A7%E5%9C%B0%E7%AD%89%E6%8E%A8%E5%BB%A3-%E6%B7%B1%E6%B0%B4%E5%9F%97%E8%87%AA%E5%8A%A9%E9%81%8A-%E6%97%85%E7%99%BC%E5%B1%80%E6%9E%97%E5%BB%BA%E5%B2%B3-%E4%B8%8D%E5%BD%B1%E9%9F%BF%E7%95%B6%E5%8D%80%E7%89%A9%E5%83%B9/</a>"},{"pid":"38503f11398fdb7f7de14423ca949b76e61e2b44","tid":814022,"uid":63909,"like":23,"dislike":0,"score":23,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-11T02:05:00.000Z","msg":"啲錢就咁洗咗去<br />\n香港洗撚去大陸推廣咩<br />\n你搵技枝鎗指住佢<br />\n佢都要黎香港買嘢架喇"},{"pid":"bcaaf91622229b43660af66a698741763d6c149e","tid":814022,"uid":57161,"like":26,"dislike":0,"score":26,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-11T02:08:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"708331dd74cb2bd3f20bba317cfb16c2faeea7da","tid":814022,"uid":28834,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-11T02:13:17.000Z","msg":"屌那星"},{"pid":"3c9aeb77b7e4535eedda92f2b6a8f032f52452e0","tid":814022,"uid":2429,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-11T02:13:30.000Z","msg":"屌你老母平時已經夠多人仲嫌唔夠迫。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ac1b657c30b2765f1f08a9ab9e8abd10b7e7fcf","tid":814022,"uid":77196,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-11T02:13:49.000Z","msg":"搞好個邊境購物城先啦局長 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkg